lenishing the substrate for NO production with L-Arg. This is the first study to demonstrate that NO plays an important role in the anti-fibrillatory effect of VNS on the rabbit ventricle, possibly via effects on APD restitution.},
author = {Brack, Kieran E and Patel, Vanlata H and Coote, John H and Ng, G Andr{\'{e}}},
